title: India launches its first space mission to the sun after lunar landing win
description: India launched Aditya-L1, its first space mission to study the sun, from Sriharikota. The spacecraft will travel to Lagrange point 1 between the sun and Earth.

title: Trump’s Truth Social facing a key funding deadline
description: With the merger stalled for months, Digital World is fast approaching a Sept. 8 deadline for the merger to close and has scheduled a shareholder vote for Tuesday to extend the deadline another year.

title: New phone sparks worry China has found a way around U.S. tech limits
description: Huawei, which has been under U.S. sanctions for years, released the phone pointedly during Gina Raimondo’s visit to Beijing
